    "actor_description": "Everything feels heavier than it should-thoughts, limbs, even breathing. I can still do things, but each action asks for a payment up front, and I keep negotiating with myself to pay it. My attention slips off details like it can't get traction, and time stretches in dull, slow sheets.",
